#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.device_print"
msgstr "# triton.language.device_print"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:4
msgid "`device_print` 用于在NPU运行时从设备端打印信息，与`static_print`不同，这是在内核执行时实时输出信息。 第一个参数必须为`string`, 后面的参数必须为`scalars`或者`tensors`。 **使用`device_print`需要将环境变量`TRITON_DEVICE_PRINT`的值设置为`True`。**"
msgstr "`device_print` is used to print information from the device side during NPU runtime. Unlike `static_print`, it outputs information in real time while the kernel is executing. The first parameter must be a `string`, and the following parameters must be `scalars` or `tensors`. **To use `device_print`, set the environment variable `TRITON_DEVICE_PRINT` to `True`.**"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.device_print(prefix, *args, hex=False, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `prefix` | `str` | 必需 | 打印值之前的前缀字符串 |\n"
"| `args` | `tensor`/`scalar` | 必需 | 要打印的值，可以是任意张量或标量 |\n"
"| `hex` | `bool` | `False` | 是否以十六进制格式打印所有值 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `prefix` | `str` | Required | Prefix string before the printed value |\n"
"| `args` | `tensor`/`scalar` | Required | Values to print, can be any tensor or scalar |\n"
"| `hex` | `bool` | `False` | Whether to print all values in hexadecimal format |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported yet |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:14
msgid "### 2.2.1 Data Type支持"
msgstr "### 2.2.1 Data Type Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:16
msgid "A3："
msgstr "A3:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:18
msgid ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:20
msgid "### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:22
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:24
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:26
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:28
msgid "Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:30
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:32
msgid "**注意**：`prefix`字符串前缀在使用`device_print`时是必须加上的，否则会导致编译错误。"
msgstr "**Note**: The `prefix` string prefix must be added when using `device_print`, otherwise it will cause a compilation error."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/device_print.md:34
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def kernel(x_ptr):\n"
"    idx = tl.arange(0,3)\n"
"    idy = tl.arange(0,4)\n"
"    offset = idx[:,None] * 4 + idy[None,:]\n"
"    val = tl.load(x_ptr + offset)\n"
"    # 打印二维张量val的值\n"
"    tl.device_print(\"val:\",val)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

